msg: Add another tag to the version number to indicate a non-release version.
svn --version --quiet will now print "0.17.0+" for a developer build, and
(SVN_VER_NUMTAG): New; a short tag for the version number.
* dist.sh: Replace the "+" in SVN_VER_NUMTAG with an empty string.
Change the version number regex to expect an optional trailing "+".
